# Copy to .env.local or .env (Vite loads both; see https://vite.dev/guide/env-and-mode.html)
#
# Leave empty to use the dev proxy: requests go to /api → http://localhost:9001 (vite.config.js).
# Set this when the API is on another origin (e.g. staging); must be a full URL without trailing slash.

# VITE_API_URL=http://localhost:9001
